      <title>保加利亚组建内阁以打破政治僵局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bulgaria-moves-forward-with-cabinet-to-break-political-deadlock</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保加利亚中右翼政党试图打破僵局，提议组建联合政府，为这个巴尔干国家提供通过有效多数解决腐败和采用欧元等问题的机会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bulgaria-moves-forward-with-cabinet-to-break-political-deadlock</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:24:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>债券市场为美国 CPI 数据做好准备</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/bond-markets-brace-for-us-cpi-data-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[隆奥银行首席信息官 Michael Strobaek 向彭博电视台表示，美国国债“正变得越来越有吸引力”。他发表此番言论之前，美国今日公布了通胀数据，预测人士预计通胀数据将连续第五个月稳步上升，这为美联储暂停降息提供了有力证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/bond-markets-brace-for-us-cpi-data-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:22:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国石油公司与伊拉克签署大部分商业条款以恢复基尔库克油田</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bp-iraq-sign-most-commercial-terms-to-revive-kirkuk-oil-field</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国石油公司和伊拉克政府周二就恢复基尔库克油田的大部分商业条款达成一致，朝着预计在今年年初达成的最终协议迈出了进一步的进展。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bp-iraq-sign-most-commercial-terms-to-revive-kirkuk-oil-field</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:18:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英伟达股价涨至 3 万亿美元，华尔街却不为所动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/nvda-nvidia-s-3-trillion-rally-is-on-edge-wall-street-is-unfazed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自 ChatGPT 帮助引发人工智能热潮以来的两年间，英伟达公司的市值增长了 3 万亿美元，这比历史上如此短时间内的任何一次股市上涨都要大。但对于这家芯片制造商来说，形势正在发生变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/nvda-nvidia-s-3-trillion-rally-is-on-edge-wall-street-is-unfazed</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 10:17:31 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
