      <title>通胀缓解市场困境，交易员加大对英国央行降息的押注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[数据显示英国12月份通胀率下降后，交易员们纷纷预测英国央行今年是否会进一步降息，缓解了人们对今年困扰英国资产的持续价格压力的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/pound-falls-as-uk-inflation-slowdown-opens-door-for-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 07:21:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国通胀放缓，股市、债市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲股市小幅走高，债券收益率下滑，因为英国通胀意外放缓，随后美国批发价格数据表现温和，令人们希望价格压力可能开始消退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-14/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 Jan 2025 22:42:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
